text: Kalanjoor is a village in Pathanamthitta district, Kerala, India. ==Demographics== As of 2001 India census, Kalanjoor had a population of 15604 with 7499 males and females. ==Educational Institutions== * College of Applied Sciences (I.H.R.D), Kalanjoor * GVHSS & GHSS Kalanjoor * Govt.
